        <item>
            <title>小米 SU7 Ultra 挑戰速度極限，時速 359.71 公里刷新全球四門量產車紀錄</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/su7-ultra/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=su7-ultra</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/su7-ultra/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 10:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米 SU7 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275570</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米汽車近日宣佈，其首款量產電動車小米 SU7 Ultra 創下了每小時 359.71 公里的驚人速度紀錄，遠超高鐵的營運速度，成為全球最快的四門量產車之一。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275576 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633-546x580.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633-546x580.jpg 546w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633.jpg 848w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 546px" /></a></p><p>小米 SU7 Ultra 性能引人注目，其搭載三電機系統，總輸出功率高達 1548 匹馬力，0 至 100 公里每小時的加速僅需 1.98 秒。在設計上，SU7 Ultra 結合碳纖維材料的車頂與側裙，以及具有運動感的菱形進氣口，進一步提升車輛的空氣動力學性能，為極速行駛提供穩定支援。</p><p>小米採用由寧德時代提供的高功率電池，峯值電壓高達 897 伏特，即使電量僅剩 20%，仍能釋放超過 800 千瓦的放電功率，並支持最高 5.2C 的充電倍率，10% 至 80% 的充電時間僅需 11 分鐘，讓日常使用更具便利性。</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">雖然小米 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">SU7 Ultra </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">售價高昂，不過 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">10 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">分鐘內獲得了 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">3680 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">台的小額訂金，追求極限的中國用户對小米 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">SU7 Ultra 仍</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">相當看好。</span></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.163.com/dy/article/JH1VQAD20511DG68.html">網易</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
